text: Very long queues were spotted here during weekends. There are many times when the queues extended into the grocery section of the store. It is hard to walk through this queue and it is very crowded. This makes it hard for the shoppers to get their groceries on weekend. It is recommended to write your 4d before going there to save time as the writing place is also very crowded.

This ntuc is at basement level of yew tee point, so its abit far to get , the ntuc finest will be nearer if just want quick grocery shopping. Usually quite crowded especially wed old folks will be there because of the elderly discount.

Queue of it makes it difficult for NTUC users to buy bread, eggs and fruits as at times queues can be super long.

It can be crowded whenever there is a big draw.
Quite crowded after 5pm throughout the week. On Tuesday, Thursday and weekend will be very crowded. There's also a lottery booth.
